This paper is about entity recommendation in search engines, which is a task related to information retrieval (IR) and natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also uses deep neural networks for representation learning, which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper uses large-scale search logs, which suggests that it may also be relevant to database systems (cs.DB).
